query: WITH entities AS (SELECT short_code_id, id FROM core_deposit_accounts WHERE (COALESCE((short_code_id, id) < ($3, $2), $2 IS NULL)) ORDER BY short_code_id DESC, id DESC LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: DepositAccountId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_deposit_account_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.short_code_id desc, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
